    "name": "Moadra",
    "steam_appid": 1713730,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713730/extras/437de934ee62a4e688bb76725fb3393c.avif?t=1769026453\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在黄沙席卷的普罗蒂亚六号行星上，穿越一个暗道纵横的巨大世界。化身魔卓拉，以你自己的步调揭开普罗蒂亚六号的冷酷谜团。经历困难重重的战斗并进化魔卓拉的技能，破解谜题，并在整个任务中揭开数不胜数的隐藏道路与秘密，从而发现失传的涅亚人遗产。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713730/extras/8f2e9b5c395cd3b95d04191d7e92e91b.webp?t=1769026453\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713730/extras/447bec6770f6ec45fdff988792821c38.poster.avif?t=1769026453\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713730/extras/447bec6770f6ec45fdff988792821c38.webm?t=1769026453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713730/extras/447bec6770f6ec45fdff988792821c38.mp4?t=1769026453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">无论你是试图体验荒芜的地表，攀登致命、严寒的山峰，还是探查爬满了恶毒外星物种的研究设施，普罗蒂亚六号上隐藏着大量可供发掘的失传秘密，它们将会揭示你的先祖在两万年前灭绝的原因。每前进一步，都有危险在等着你。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713730/extras/d2c6d05425815bc906be778d0934766d.webp?t=1769026453\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713730/extras/1d7a81ebdc94a7897e1ac818f4b719e3.poster.avif?t=1769026453\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713730/extras/1d7a81ebdc94a7897e1ac818f4b719e3.webm?t=1769026453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713730/extras/1d7a81ebdc94a7897e1ac818f4b719e3.mp4?t=1769026453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">借助魔卓拉的机敏灵活来翻滚、躲闪、跳跃、飞檐走壁，并以前所未有的速度冲刺，从而躲避致命的有机体和有害的恶劣天气。利用你的迅捷反应力、丰富的武器库以及特殊技能来全力求生，应对各种各样的低级别威胁，乃至会逼你使出浑身解数的巨怪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713730/extras/db797763b3dccbbcb74ae075e7a88e03.webp?t=1769026453\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713730/extras/cf0f798ca3b3f1413b74a1222c09aa3b.poster.avif?t=1769026453\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713730/extras/cf0f798ca3b3f1413b74a1222c09aa3b.webm?t=1769026453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713730/extras/cf0f798ca3b3f1413b74a1222c09aa3b.mp4?t=1769026453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">启动你的扫描仪机器人，使用X射线视野来更仔细地检查生物和你身处的环境。揭晓隐藏道路和肉眼不可见的秘密区域，并勾勒出已探索的地图片区。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">轰飞不怀好意的生物和有机体以吸收其普罗托浆——一种充满能量的生物质包块。在有机腔室内消耗此物质来实现变形，并将你的技能和武器进化至新的等级。  </p>",
